uk.ac.qmul.sbcs.evolution.convergence.handlers.documents.parsers.codeml

Class CodemlParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.qmul.sbcs.evolution.convergence.handlers.documents.parsers.codeml.CodemlParser
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CodemlParserBranchSite, CodemlParserCladeC, CodemlParserM1, CodemlParserM2

    public abstract class CodemlParser
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstract class defining actions of a CodemlParser.

    Implementation detail of parsing for each model (M0, M1, Clade Model C etc) handled by constructor. Default constructor should be with java.lang.util.ArrayList<String> input data.

    Resulting CodemlModel is returned with CodemlParser.getModelData() call.

    Author:
    Joe Parker, Kitson Consulting / Queen Mary University of London
    See Also:
    CodemlModel, CodemlResultReader, ArrayList, BasicFileReader, CapitalisedFileReader
